'''Pollo''' (sometimes stylized as '''POLLO''')<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://ego.globo.com/famosos/noticia/2013/09/apos-sumico-adriel-da-banda-pollo-diz-que-banda-nao-vai-acabar.html |title=EGO - Após sumiço, Adriel, da banda Pollo, diz que banda não vai acabar - notícias de Famosos |publisher=Ego.globo.com |date=2013-09-17 |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref> is a rap group<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zerohora.clicrbs.com.br/rs/cultura-e-lazer/segundo-caderno/noticia/2013/06/rap-da-pollo-abre-o-atlantida-festival-4171541.html |title=Rap da Pollo abre o Atlântida Festival - Entretenimento - Zero Hora - Entretenimento - Zero Hora |publisher=Zerohora.clicrbs.com.br |date=2013-06-15 |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref> formed in 2010 in São Paulo by the MCs Luiz Tomim (also known as “Tomim”), Adriel de Menezes (also known as "AdR"), and DJ Kalfani.<ref name="webdahora">{{cite web|url=http://www.webdahora.com/musicas/banda-pollo-brasil-biografia-videoclipes-musicas-famosas|title=Pollo Biografia|publisher=Webdahora.com|accessdate=20 January 2013|last=|first=}}</ref> The band found fame with its hit “Vagalumes”, which has had over 30 million views on [[YouTube]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://entretenimento.r7.com/musica/fotos/pollo-estoura-com-vagalumes-vai-ser-o-unico-hit-do-grupo-relembre-artistas-que-tiveram-um-so-sucesso-07062013#!/foto/1 |title=Pollo estoura com Vagalumes. Vai ser o único hit do grupo? Relembre artistas que tiveram um só sucesso - Fotos - R7 Música |publisher=Entretenimento.r7.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://musica.uol.com.br/noticias/redacao/2013/05/27/formada-por-bandas-como-pollo-e-bonde-da-stronda-a-cena-do-rap-mostra-seu-lado-mais-pop.htm?mobile |title=Formada por bandas como Pollo e Bonde da Stronda, cena do rap mostra seu lado mais pop - Últimas Notícias - UOL Música |publisher=Musica.uol.com.br |date= |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref> In September 2013, after the disappearance of Adriel Luis Tomim, DJ Kalfani and Luiz Tomim announced they were fulfilling the touring schedule and commitments until 31 December 2013, when they would disband and stop performing.<ref name="saídadeintegrantes">{{cite web|title='Ano novo, vida nova', diz o cantor Tomim sobre fim da banda Pollo|url=http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/musica/noticia/2013/09/ano-novo-vida-nova-diz-o-cantor-tomim-sobre-fim-da-banda-pollo.html|publisher=[[Globo.com]]|accessdate=13 September 2013|date=12 September 2013}}</ref> Three days later, after a decision by the remaining band members, Adriel stated that the band would not discontinue.

==Biography==

===2011-2012: Vim Pra Dominar o Mundo===
The group was originally formed in 2010, recording and writing entirely in a home production environment, and distributing their music via the Internet. The first song which was professionally studio recorded was "Trama", in 2010. Pollo became known on the Internet for the song "Zica do Bagui", from collaborator [[Bonde da Stronda]]. In 2012, they announced a new member, DJ Kalfani, son of KL Jay from [[Racionais MC’s]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jovem.ig.com.br/cultura/musica/2012-12-05/pollo-os-racionais-falavam-de-violencia-mas-nos-queremos-falar-de-amor.html|title=Pollo Biografia / tudo sobre a banda pollo|publisher=jovem.ig.com.br|accessdate= 25 January 2013|last=|first=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://g1.globo.com/musica/noticia/2013/05/base-e-rap-mas-curtimos-misturar-diz-pollo-sobre-hit-em-sangue-bom.html |title=G1 - 'Base é rap, mas curtimos misturar', diz Pollo sobre hit em 'Sangue bom' - notícias em Música |publisher=G1.globo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref>
In 2012, the group released the clips "Trama", "Pirituba City", "As Quatro", "Buxixos & Simpatias", and "Vagalumes".

According to Brasil Hot Airplay,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mixtv.com.br/programas/plantaomix/veja-os-vencedores-do-melhores-de-2012-da-mix-tv/|title=single da banda pollo vagalumes, vensedor em musica e e videoclipe do ano - mixtv|publisher=Mixtv.com.br|accessdate=2013-01-20|last=|first=}}</ref> the song "Vagalumes" was one of the most requested songs on radio. It was also included in the soundtrack of [[Rede Globo]]'s telenovela ''[[Sangue Bom]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://contigo.abril.com.br/noticias/teen/tudo-que-falamos-na-nossa-musica-estamos-vivendo-diz-lider-da-banda-pollo-dona-do-hit-vagalumes |title="Tudo o que falamos na nossa música estamos vivendo" diz líder da banda Pollo, dona do hit Vagalume - Acontece - Novelas e Famosos - MdeMulher - Editora Abril |publisher=Contigo.abril.com.br |date= |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://ego.globo.com/ego-teen/noticia/2013/06/cache-foi-vodka-lembram-meninos-da-pollo-donos-do-hit-vagalumes.html |title=EGO - 'Cachê foi vodca', lembram meninos da Pollo, donos do hit 'Vagalumes' - notícias de Ego Teen |publisher=Ego.globo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mais.uol.com.br/view/u7koy1tz917d/pollo-comemora-musica-vagalumes-em-novela-e-toca-ao-vivo-04028C1A3266C4A14326?types=A& |title=UOL Mais > Pollo comemora música "Vagalumes" em novela e toca ao vivo |language=pt|publisher=Mais.uol.com.br |date=2013-04-19 |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Torricelli Medeiros |url=http://www.midiatotal.net/2013/03/vagalumes-pollo-part-ivo-mozart.html |title=Vagalumes - Pollo - Tema de Giane em Sangue Bom! |publisher=Midiatotal.net |date=2014-03-30 |accessdate=2014-06-27}}</ref> With the participation of singer Ivo Mozart,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://noticias.r7.com/legendarios/videos/pollo-canta-o-rap-vagalumes-/idmedia/509e1122b61c8af7a8dcb625.html|title=Pollo na TV Record|publisher=noticias.r7.com|accessdate=20 January 2013}}</ref> the song was nominated in, and won, the categories of best song and music video of the year. The song currently has over 30 million views on [[YouTube]]. In the same year, the band released their first album titled "Vim Para Dominar o Mundo" which could be downloaded for free on [[iTunes]].<ref name="webdahora" /><ref name="virgula">{{cite web|last=Rabassallo|first=Luciana|url=http://virgula.uol.com.br/ver/noticia/musica/2013/02/18/319720-hit-no-youtube-grupo-pollo-explica-sucesso-repentino-nao-estariamos-aqui-sem-a-internet#0|title=Hit no Youtube, grupo Pollo explica sucesso repentino: "Não estaríamos aqui sem a internet"|date=19 February 2013|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://noticias.r7.com/legendarios/videos/menino-dos-pollo-falam-com-exclusividade-para-o-legendarios-na-web/idmedia/509e1adcfc9b132ef81f45f8.html|title=Banda Pollo|publisher=noticias.r7.com|accessdate=20 January 2013|last=|first=}}</ref><ref name="mtv_vim">{{cite web|url=http://mtv.uol.com.br/musica/pollo-lanca-1-disco-e-vai-muito-alem-de-pirituba-city|title=Pollo CD Vim Pra Dominar o Mundo MTV|publisher=mtv.uol.com.br|accessdate=20 January 2013 |last=|first=}}</ref><ref name="redetv_lanca">{{cite web|url=http://www.redetv.com.br/Video.aspx?117,30,308202,entretenimento,redetvi-entretenimento,banda-pollo-explica-lancamento-nacional-de-cd-em-121212|title=RedeTV - Pollo   Banda Pollo explica lançamento nacional de CD em 12/12/12 na RedeTV|publisher=www.redetv.com.br|accessdate=15 February 2013|last=|first=}}</ref>

===2013–present===
In 2014, the band released a new album, under the label [[Som Livre]], called "777".

